data.description: Great property in town, Mackay. 3 bd 2bth manufactured home with nice layout, Spacious kitchen, dining and living area. Master suite with walk-in closet. Established lawn with trees and flower beds. Large covered deck, partially screened to enjoy the outdoors. Large shop and covered carport. Close to the Mackay golf course. A great spot to enjoy all this area has to offer.
